GhostTrack turns common OSINT checks into one CLI workflow. Instead of jumping between separate sites, you can look up IP data, phone metadata, and username presence in one place. It’s practical for quick verification, triage, and first-pass digital investigation.

https://github.com/HunxByts/GhostTrack

